{"data":[{"name":"74:1","price":"Ô, toi (Mohammed) ! Le revêtu d’un manteau !","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡمُدَّثِّرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5496,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:2","price":"Lève-toi et avertis.","arabic":"قُمۡ فَأَنذِرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5497,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:3","price":"Et de ton Seigneur, célèbre la grandeur.","arabic":"وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5498,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:4","price":"Et tes vêtements, purifie-les.","arabic":"وَثِيَابَكَ فَطَهِّرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5499,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:5","price":"Et de tout péché, écarte-toi .","arabic":"وَٱلرُّجۡزَ فَٱهۡجُرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5500,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[998] De tout péché: (autre sens) fuis les idoles.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:6","price":"Et ne donne pas dans le but de recevoir davantage .","arabic":"وَلَا تَمۡنُن تَسۡتَكۡثِرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5501,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[999] Autre sens: ne surestime pas tes actes.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:7","price":"Et pour ton Seigneur, endure.","arabic":"وَلِرَبِّكَ فَٱصۡبِرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5502,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:8","price":"Quand on sonnera du Clairon,","arabic":"فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِي ٱلنَّاقُورِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5503,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:9","price":"alors, ce jour-là sera un jour difficile,","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ يَوۡمَئِذٖ يَوۡمٌ عَسِيرٌ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5504,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:10","price":"pas facile pour les mécréants.","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ غَيۡرُ يَسِيرٖ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5505,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:11","price":"Laisse-Moi avec celui que J’ai créé seul [1000],","arabic":"ذَرۡنِي وَمَنۡ خَلَقۡتُ وَحِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5506,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1000] Celui que J’ai crée seul: Il s’agit de «Al-Walīd Ibn al-Mughīrah». Seul: autre interprétation: Moi Allah tout Seul.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:12","price":"et à qui J’ai donné des biens étendus,","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡتُ لَهُۥ مَالٗا مَّمۡدُودٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5507,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:13","price":"et des enfants qui lui tiennent toujours compagnie,","arabic":"وَبَنِينَ شُهُودٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5508,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:14","price":"pour qui aussi J’ai aplani toutes difficultés.","arabic":"وَمَهَّدتُّ لَهُۥ تَمۡهِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5509,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:15","price":"Cependant, il convoite [de Moi] que Je lui donne davantage.","arabic":"ثُمَّ يَطۡمَعُ أَنۡ أَزِيدَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5510,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:16","price":"Pas du tout ! Car il reniait nos versets (le Coran) avec entêtement.","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ لِأٓيَٰتِنَا عَنِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5511,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:17","price":"Je vais le contraindre à gravir une pente.","arabic":"سَأُرۡهِقُهُۥ صَعُودًا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5512,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:18","price":"Il a réfléchi. Et il a décidé.","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ فَكَّرَ وَقَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5513,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:19","price":"Qu’il périsse ! Comme il a décidé !","arabic":"فَقُتِلَ كَيۡفَ قَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5514,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:20","price":"Encore une fois, qu’il périsse; comme il a décidé !","arabic":"ثُمَّ قُتِلَ كَيۡفَ قَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5515,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:21","price":"Ensuite, il a regardé.","arabic":"ثُمَّ نَظَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5516,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:22","price":"Et il s’est renfrogné et a durci son visage.","arabic":"ثُمَّ عَبَسَ وَبَسَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5517,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:23","price":"Ensuite il a tourné le dos et s’est enflé d’orgueil.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ وَٱسۡتَكۡبَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5518,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:24","price":"Puis il a dit : \"Ceci (le Coran) n’est que magie apprise.","arabic":"فَقَالَ إِنۡ هَٰذَآ إِلَّا سِحۡرٞ يُؤۡثَرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5519,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:25","price":"ce n’est là que la parole d’un humain.\"","arabic":"إِنۡ هَٰذَآ إِلَّا قَوۡلُ ٱلۡبَشَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5520,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:26","price":"Je vais le brûler dans le Feu intense (Saqar).","arabic":"سَأُصۡلِيهِ سَقَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5521,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:27","price":"Et qui te dira ce qu’est Saqar ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا سَقَرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5522,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:28","price":"Il ne laisse rien et n’épargne rien ;","arabic":"لَا تُبۡقِي وَلَا تَذَرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5523,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:29","price":"Il brûle la peau et la noircit.","arabic":"لَوَّاحَةٞ لِّلۡبَشَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5524,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:30","price":"Ils sont dix-neuf à y veiller [1001].","arabic":"عَلَيۡهَا تِسۡعَةَ عَشَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5525,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1001] Il s’agit des dix neuf Anges préposés à Saqar.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:31","price":"Nous n’avons assigné comme gardiens du Feu que les Anges. Cependant, Nous n’en avons fixé le nombre que pour éprouver les mécréants, et aussi afin que ceux à qui le Livre a été apporté soient convaincus, et que croisse la foi de ceux qui croient, et que ceux à qui le Livre a été apporté et les croyants n’aient point de doute ; et pour que ceux qui ont au cœur quelque maladie ainsi que les mécréants disent : \"Qu’a donc voulu Allah par cette parabole ?\" C’est ainsi qu’Allah égare qui Il veut et guide qui Il veut. Nul ne connaît les armées de ton Seigneur, à part Lui. Et ce n’est là qu’un rappel pour les humains.","arabic":"وَمَا جَعَلۡنَآ أَصۡحَٰبَ ٱلنَّارِ إِلَّا مَلَٰٓئِكَةٗۖ وَمَا جَعَلۡنَا عِدَّتَهُمۡ إِلَّا فِتۡنَةٗ لِّلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ لِيَسۡتَيۡقِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ أُوتُواْ ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ وَيَزۡدَادَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓاْ إِيمَٰنٗا وَلَا يَرۡتَابَ ٱلَّذِينَ أُوتُواْ ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ وَٱلۡمُؤۡمِنُونَ وَلِيَقُولَ ٱلَّذِينَ فِي قُلُوبِهِم مَّرَضٞ وَٱلۡكَٰفِرُونَ مَاذَآ أَرَادَ ٱللَّهُ بِهَٰذَا مَثَلٗاۚ كَذَٰلِكَ يُضِلُّ ٱللَّهُ مَن يَشَآءُ وَيَهۡدِي مَن يَشَآءُۚ وَمَا يَعۡلَمُ جُنُودَ رَبِّكَ إِلَّا هُوَۚ وَمَا هِيَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرَىٰ لِلۡبَشَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5526,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:32","price":"Non !... Par la lune !","arabic":"كَلَّا وَٱلۡقَمَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5527,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:33","price":"Et par la nuit quand elle se retire !","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذۡ أَدۡبَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5528,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:34","price":"Et par l’aurore quand elle se découvre !","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَآ أَسۡفَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5529,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:35","price":"[Saqar] est l’un des plus grands [malheurs]","arabic":"إِنَّهَا لَإِحۡدَى ٱلۡكُبَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5530,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:36","price":"un avertissement, pour les humains.","arabic":"نَذِيرٗا لِّلۡبَشَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5531,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:37","price":"Pour qui d’entre vous, veut avancer ou reculer.","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَتَقَدَّمَ أَوۡ يَتَأَخَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5532,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:38","price":"Toute âme est l’otage de ce qu’elle a acquis.","arabic":"كُلُّ نَفۡسِۭ بِمَا كَسَبَتۡ رَهِينَةٌ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5533,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:39","price":"Sauf les gens de la droite (les élus) :","arabic":"إِلَّآ أَصۡحَٰبَ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5534,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:40","price":"dans des Jardins, ils s’interrogeront.","arabic":"فِي جَنَّٰتٖ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5535,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:41","price":"au sujet des criminels:","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5536,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:42","price":"\"Qu’est-ce qui vous a acheminés à Saqar ?\"","arabic":"مَا سَلَكَكُمۡ فِي سَقَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5537,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:43","price":"Ils diront : \"Nous n’étions pas de ceux qui faisaient la prière (As-Salât),","arabic":"قَالُواْ لَمۡ نَكُ مِنَ ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5538,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:44","price":"et nous ne nourrissions pas le pauvre,","arabic":"وَلَمۡ نَكُ نُطۡعِمُ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5539,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:45","price":"et nous nous associions à ceux qui tenaient des conversations futiles,","arabic":"وَكُنَّا نَخُوضُ مَعَ ٱلۡخَآئِضِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5540,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:46","price":"et nous traitions de mensonge le jour de la Rétribution,","arabic":"وَكُنَّا نُكَذِّبُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5541,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:47","price":"jusqu’à ce que nous vînt la vérité évidente [la mort].\"","arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ أَتَىٰنَا ٱلۡيَقِينُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5542,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:48","price":"Ne leur profitera point donc, l’intercession des intercesseurs.","arabic":"فَمَا تَنفَعُهُمۡ شَفَٰعَةُ ٱلشَّٰفِعِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5543,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:49","price":"Qu’ont-ils à se détourner du Rappel ?","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُمۡ عَنِ ٱلتَّذۡكِرَةِ مُعۡرِضِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5544,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:50","price":"Ils sont comme des onagres épouvantés,","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ حُمُرٞ مُّسۡتَنفِرَةٞ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5545,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:51","price":"s’enfuyant devant un lion.","arabic":"فَرَّتۡ مِن قَسۡوَرَةِۭ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5546,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:52","price":"Chacun d’eux voudrait plutôt qu’on lui apporte des feuilles tout étalées.","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُؤۡتَىٰ صُحُفٗا مُّنَشَّرَةٗ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5547,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:53","price":"Ah ! Non ! C’est plutôt qu’ils ne craignent pas l’au-delà.","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ بَل لَّا يَخَافُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5548,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:54","price":"Ah ! Non ! Ceci est vraiment un Rappel.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهُۥ تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5549,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:55","price":"Quiconque veut, qu’il se le rappelle.","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5550,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"74:56","price":"Mais ils ne se rappelleront que si Allah veut. C’est Lui qui est Le plus digne d’être craint; et c’est Lui qui détient le pardon.","arabic":"وَمَا يَذۡكُرُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ هُوَ أَهۡلُ ٱلتَّقۡوَىٰ وَأَهۡلُ ٱلۡمَغۡفِرَةِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5551,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir","Chapter Al-Muddathir","Muddathir","Surah Muddathir","Chapter Muddathir","Al Muddathir","Surah Al Muddathir","Chapter Al Muddathir","Surah 74","Chapter 74","The Cloaked One","المدثر"]}